        <title>何以逻辑自洽的生活</title>
        <link>https://Elysium-Seeker.github.io/p/%E4%BD%95%E4%BB%A5%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E8%87%AA%E6%B4%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/</link>
